# Asset context is the repo root (CDK fromAsset('..')). Exclude the CDK
# output/deps so the container-asset staging does not recurse into cdk.out
# (which lives at cdk/cdk.out, inside this same context) → ENAMETOOLONG.
cdk/cdk.out
cdk/node_modules
**/node_modules
.git
.gitignore
docker
docker-compose.yml
